Pulao :

1 cup rice , cinnamon - 1 , cardamom -2 , clove 2-3 
mediu size onion -1 , chilli - 1 
potato - 1/2 cup 
carrot 
peas 

instant pot - saute 1 tbspn 
ghee 1 spoon 
bay leave cinnamon etc
stir 
add onion stir until golden brown
stir add veggies including peas 
1/2 tbspn turmeric
saute for 1 minute 
water 1-1,5 cup 
salt 
add washed rice 
mint or coriander leaves 
cancel saute , close and seal 
high pressure 6 minute and quick release pressure 

